<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 28. Collecting sites of Diduga spp. Key: D. simianshana sp. nov.: China, Chongqing, Mt Simian (blue dot); D. chebalinga sp. nov.: China, Prov. Guangdong, Shaoguan, Chebaling (red dot); D. chewi sp. nov. and D. hollowayi sp. nov.: Malaysia, Borneo (both green dot)." , "Figures 22 - 27. Female genitalia of Diduga spp. 22 D. simianshana sp. nov., paratype, genit. prep. No. ztt- 073 - 2 23 D. chebalinga sp. nov., paratype, genit. prep. No. ztt- 077 - 2 24 D. quinquicornuta (after Bayarsaikhan and Bae 2019) 25 D. chewi sp. nov., paratype, genit. prep. No. ztt- 102 - 2 26 D. hollowayi sp. nov., paratype, genit. prep. No. ztt- 083 - 2 27 D. kohkongensis (after Bayarsaikhan & Bae, 2018). Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figures 18 - 21. Male genitalia of Diduga spp. 18 D. chewi sp. nov., holotype, genit. prep. No. ztt- 110 - 1 19 D. trichophora (after Bucsek 2012) 20 D. hollowayi sp. nov., holotype, genit. prep. No. ztt- 033 - 1 21 D. kohkongensis (after Bayarsaikhan & Bae, 2018). Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figures 7 - 12. Adults of Diduga spp. 7 D. chewi sp. nov., male, holotype, Malaysia (Borneo) 8 ditto, female, paratype, Malaysia (Borneo) 9 D. trichophora, male (after Bucsek 2012) 10 D. kohkongensis, male (after Bayarsaikhan & Bae, 2018) 11 D. hollowayi sp. nov., male, holotype, Malaysia (Borneo) 12 ditto, female, paratype, Malaysia (Borneo)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/471892" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/471891" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/471890" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/471887" .

